ete chloroplast genome sequence of a tree fern Alsophila spinulosa: insights into evolutionary changes in fern chloroplast genomes | journal = BMC Evolutionary Biology | volume = 9 | issue =  | pages = 130 | date = June 2009 | pmid = 19519899 | pmc = 2706227 | doi = 10.1186/1471-2148-9-130 }}</ref>\n|[[Cyatheaceae]]\n|-\n|''[[Angiopteris]] [[Angiopteris evecta|evecta]]''\n|\n|153,901\n|\n|<ref name=\"roper2007\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Roper JM, Hansen SK, Wolf PG, Karol KG, Mandoli DF, Everett KD, Kuehl J, Boore JL | year = 2007 | title = The Complete Plastid Genome Sequence of ''Angiopteris evecta'' (G. Forst.) Hoffm. (Marattiaceae) | url = | journal = American Fern Journal | volume = 97 | issue = 2| pages = 95\u2013106 | doi = 10.1640/0002-8444(2007)97[95:TCPGSO]2.0.CO;2 | doi-access = free }}</ref> \n|[[Marattiaceae]]\n|-\n|''[[Equisetum]] [[Equisetum arvense|arvense]]''\n|\n|133,309\n|\n|\n|[[Equisetaceae]]\n|-\n|''[[Huperzia]] [[Huperzia lucidula|lucidula]]''\n|\n|154,373\n|\n|<ref name=\"wolf2005\">{{cite journal | vauthors = Wolf PG, Karol KG, Mandoli DF, Kuehl J, Arumuganathan K, Ellis MW, Mishler BD, Kelch DG, Olmstead RG, Boore JL | title = The first complete chloroplast genome sequence of a lycophyte, Huperzia lucidula (Lycopodiaceae) | journal = Gene | volume = 350 | issue = 2 | pages = 117\u201328 | date = May 2005 | pmid = 15788152 | doi = 10.1016/j.gene.2005.01.018 | url = https://digital.library.unt.edu/ark:/67531/metadc779107/ }}</ref>\n|[[Lycopodiaceae]]\n|-\n|''[[Isoetes]] [[Isoetes flaccida|flaccida]]''\n|\n|145,303\n|\n|\n|[[Isoetaceae]]\n|-\n|''[[Psilotum]] [[Psilotum nudum|nudum]]''\n|\n|138,829\n|117\n|<ref name=\"wakasugi1998\">{{cite journal | author=Wakasugi, T|year=1998 |url=https://ci.nii.ac.jp/naid/10020145132/ |title=Complete nucleotide sequence of the plastid genome from a fern, ''Psilotum nudum'' |journal=Endocytobiology and Cell Research |volume=13 |issue=Supplement |pages=147}} See ''External links'' below.</ref>\n|[[Psilotace